| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2515 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 51f68879-0d3b-523d-9dac-17d2f8387892"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
